data.description: **NOT FOR RENT** This is your opportunity to own an elegantly remodeled beautiful golf course home in the coveted Town of Sun City! This home has gorgeous upgrades throughout, especially the custom redesigned new kitchen white shaker cabinets with stunning quartz countertops & fixtures, new stainless steel appliances, new bathroom, flooring & sliding glass rear entry door. Additionally, a new sewer line was installed in 2022. This home offers a spectacular view of the Sun City North Golf Course! This home is move in ready for year round residents or lock & leave seasonal home! Very little maintenance is required on the front and back yard.
